Package io.papermc.paper.entity.damage

Class VanillaDamageOrigin

java.lang.Object
io.papermc.paper.entity.damage.VanillaDamageOrigin
public final class VanillaDamageOrigin extends Object
A static collection and helper methods to retrieve the already existing damage origin. Those exist also for equality between the event cause and the vanilla cause.
